                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Olney</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Taylor</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 1, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Urge Spanish foreign office to at once instruct Captain-General Cuba to strictly
                    observe protocol applicable to trial of American citizens found on board <hi
                        rend="italic">Competitor</hi>. This cable sent at instance of Consul-General
                    Williams. Cable result.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
